OL,3,C'I didn't know if she was alive':
OL,4,CBritish couple on their Taliban
OL,5,Cimprisonment
OL,7,FA British man arrested in Afghanistan
OL,8,Falongside his wife has said he did not
OL,9,Fknow if she was alive as they spent
OL,10,Fnearly eight months in prison.
OL,12,FPeter and Barbie Reynolds were
OL,13,Farrested as they travelled to their
OL,14,Fhome in Bamyan province, central
OL,15,FAfghanistan, having lived in the
OL,16,Fcountry for 18 years running a
OL,17,Ftraining and education organisation.
