OL,3,C'I didn't know if she was alive':
OL,4,CBritish couple on their Taliban
OL,5,Cimprisonment
OL,7,FTheir circumstances changed when the
OL,8,FTaliban took control of the country in
OL,9,F2021 but unlike many international
OL,10,Fpeople living in Afghanistan, they
OL,11,Fdecided not to flee.
OL,13,F"The hardest thing for me was not
OL,14,Fhaving contact with this gorgeous lady
OL,15,Fhere," Peter Reynolds said, gesturing
OL,16,Fat his wife during an interview on
OL,17,FGood Morning Britain. "I didn't know
OL,18,Fwhether they were brutally treating
OL,19,Fher, I really just didn't know."
