OL,3,C'I didn't know if she was alive':
OL,4,CBritish couple on their Taliban
OL,5,Cimprisonment
OL,7,FPeter was in a maximum security prison
OL,8,Fand at one point was handcuffed to a
OL,9,Fman who had killed his wife and
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FBoth were held in cells for weeks
OL,13,Fwithout sunlight.
OL,15,FTheir daughter Sarah acted as a
OL,16,Fcommunicator between the two as she
OL,17,Fwas able to phone each while they had
OL,18,Fno contact with one another.
