OL,7,F"It was definitely a scary time, and I
OL,8,Fwas passing love messages between the
OL,9,Ftwo of them."
OL,11,F"It was always 'tell him I love her'
OL,12,For 'tell him I miss him'," she said.
OL,14,FBarbie still has a spoon that she
OL,15,Freceived in the first prison when
OL,16,Fpeople "took pity on her" as she was
OL,17,Fstruggling to eat without cutlery, one
OL,18,Fof her only possessions over those
OL,19,Feight months.
