OL,7,FShe learned how to use a spoon to do
OL,8,Feverything - as a knife, fork, potato
OL,9,Fpeeler and even as a means of frying
OL,10,Feggs.
OL,12,FPeter and Barbie Reynolds have
OL,13,Fdescribed their experience in Taliban
OL,14,Fprison and how they now feel about the
OL,15,Fcountry they had called home for 18
OL,16,Fyears
OL,18,FDespite their experiences, Barbie and
OL,19,FPeter believe that Afghanistan can
OL,20,Fmove away from its current
OL,21,Ftotalitarian regime.
