OL,7,F"We have had a conviction that
OL,8,FAfghanistan can change and it could
OL,9,Fjust amaze the world," Peter said.
OL,11,F"Instead of being a dysfunctional
OL,12,Fplace where the world sees it as being
OL,13,Fa place of violence, kidnappings,
OL,14,Fransoms, drug abuse... Instead of
OL,15,Fthat, there would be a miracle happen
OL,16,Fwith this dysfunctional nation."
