OL,7,F"I really do feel for the people... I
OL,8,Fthink (our imprisonment) will be
OL,9,Fanother thing that will be very
OL,10,Fdiscouraging... If the government is
OL,11,Fjust controlling, it is very difficult
OL,12,Ffor people," Barbie added.
OL,14,FThe pair only found out they were
OL,15,Fgoing to be released an hour before
OL,16,Fthe jet bringing them to the UK took
OL,17,Foff.
