OL,7,FThey arrived at Heathrow Airport on
OL,8,FSaturday afternoon and have said they
OL,9,Fare now taking life "one hour at a
OL,10,Ftime".
OL,12,FBarbie and Peter's release came after
OL,13,Fmonths of campaigning by the couple's
OL,14,Fchildren.
