OL,7,FIn a statement on Friday, the family
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are overwhelmed with
OL,9,Fgratitude and relief to share that our
OL,10,Fparents, Peter and Barbie Reynolds,
OL,11,Fhave been released after seven months
OL,12,Fand 21 days in detention by the
OL,13,FTaliban.
OL,15,F"This is a moment of immense joy for
OL,16,Four family, and we are deeply thankful
OL,17,Fto everyone who played a role in
OL,18,Fsecuring their release."
OL,20,FThe Taliban have never explained what
OL,21,Fprompted the couple's detention.
